WEBVTT

00:10:58.548 --> 00:11:02.184
that adapts and evolves
a lot quicker than we do.

00:11:02.980 --> 00:11:04.520
And in that war,

00:11:04.544 --> 00:11:09.043
this little spider might be
one of our greatest secret weapons.

00:11:09.819 --> 00:11:13.787
Just a half a millionth
of a liter of a venom,

00:11:13.811 --> 00:11:16.867
diluted 10,000 times,

00:11:16.891 --> 00:11:22.121
is still capable of killing most bacteria

00:11:22.145 --> 00:11:25.518
that are resistant
to any other kind of antibiotics.

00:11:26.006 --> 00:11:27.511
It's absolutely amazing.

00:11:27.535 --> 00:11:31.576
Every time I repeat
this experiment, I just wonder: